---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SOCIAL_LINKS } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="About Twin Cities Dad - a father documenting life in Minnesota during these challenging times." />
		<style>
			.about-container {
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
			}
			
			.about-header {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}
			
			.about-header h1 {
				font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}
			
			.about-header p {
				color: var(--text-muted);
				font-size: 1.1rem;
			}
			
			.about-content {
				background: var(--bg-secondary);
				border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
				padding: 2.5rem;
				border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
			}
			
			.about-content h2 {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				margin-top: 2rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				color: var(--text-primary);
			}
			
			.about-content h2:first-child {
				margin-top: 0;
			}
			
			.about-content p {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				line-height: 1.8;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}
			
			.about-content ul {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				padding-left: 1.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}
			
			.about-content li {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			
			.connect-section {
				margin-top: 2.5rem;
				padding-top: 2rem;
				border-top: 1px solid var(--bg-tertiary);
			}
			
			.connect-section h2 {
				margin-top: 0;
			}
			
			.social-buttons {
				display: flex;
				gap: 1rem;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				margin-top: 1.5rem;
			}
			
			.social-btn {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.75rem;
				padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
				background: var(--bg-tertiary);
				border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
				color: var(--text-primary);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
				transition: all var(--transition-fast);
			}
			
			.social-btn:hover {
				transform: translateY(-2px);
				text-decoration: none;
			}
			
			.social-btn.twitter:hover {
				background: #1DA1F2;
			}
			
			.social-btn.facebook:hover {
				background: #1877F2;
			}
			
			.social-btn.instagram:hover {
				background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f09433, #e6683c, #dc2743, #cc2366, #bc1888);
			}
			
			.social-btn svg {
				width: 20px;
				height: 20px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="container">
			<div class="about-container">
				<header class="about-header">
					<h1>üëã About Me</h1>
					<p>A father in Minnesota navigating these turbulent times.</p>
				</header>
				
				<div class="about-content">
					<h2>Why This Blog?</h2>
					<p>
						I'm a dad living in the Twin Cities, and like many of you, I've been watching the world 
						change around us at a dizzying pace. Between raising kids, working, and trying to stay 
						informed, it's a lot to process.
					</p>
					<p>
						This blog is my attempt to make sense of it all. I write about what I see happening in 
						Minnesota‚Äîthe politics, the community events, the challenges, and yes, the hope too. 
						I try to back up my observations with facts and data, because in an age of 
						misinformation, truth matters more than ever.
					</p>
					
					<h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>üèõÔ∏è <strong>Political Analysis</strong> ‚Äî Making sense of what's happening at the state and local level</li>
						<li>üìä <strong>Facts & Data</strong> ‚Äî Evidence-based perspectives, not just opinions</li>
						<li>üì∞ <strong>News Commentary</strong> ‚Äî Breaking down the stories that matter to families</li>
						<li>üè° <strong>Community Stories</strong> ‚Äî What it's really like raising kids here</li>
						<li>üìπ <strong>Videos & Media</strong> ‚Äî Visual stories from around the Twin Cities</li>
					</ul>
					
					<h2>A Father's Perspective</h2>
					<p>
						Everything I write comes through the lens of being a parent. What does this policy mean 
						for our schools? How does this decision affect our neighborhoods? What kind of Minnesota 
						are we leaving for our children?
					</p>
					<p>
						These are the questions that keep me up at night, and they're the questions I try to 
						explore here. I don't have all the answers, but I believe in the power of honest 
						conversation and community.
					</p>
					
					<div class="connect-section">
						<h2>Connect With Me</h2>
						<p>I'd love to hear from you. Follow along on social media, share your thoughts, and let's build a conversation about what matters.</p>
						<div class="social-buttons">
							<a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.twitter} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-btn twitter">
